"Ego is the fifth single off the famed I Am . . . Sasha Fierce album. The music video premiered on Beyonce's official website May 21.

Ego like Single Ladies, If I Were A Boy and Diva is shot in black and white. The video is of Beyonce a 2 back-up dancers performing various routines around a chair. Beyonce is seen with a permed hairstyle to go with the RnB EGO style.
